ives.We would like to invite WWW2012 registrants to attend as many sessions in the Demo Track as your schedule allows. Many of the demo presenters have also consented to repeat their presentations and host faceto- face discussions in an area specifically designated in the exhibition hall. In a joint experiment with the IW3C2, some of the demonstrations will even be available in the virtual world Second Life.},
